      </article>

      <article class="testimonial-card hidden-review">
        <p>"Their attention to detail is unmatched. I always recommend them to my peers."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="author-info">
            Lisa W. <span class="stars">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <img src="images/lisa.jpg" alt="Lisa W." class="author-img">
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="testimonial-card hidden-review">
        <p>"I’ve been able to scale faster thanks to their reliable services."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="author-info">
